Build-vs-Buy Decision Tree Flowchart: Start node "Neues LLM-Projekt" -> Decision nodes based on: Datenhoheit? (Ja -> Self-hosted, Nein -> Cloud API), Scale? (>1M/day -> Self-hosted/Hybrid), Latenz? (<100ms -> Edge/Cloud Inference), Regulierung? (Reguliert -> Self-hosted+PII). End nodes with recommended deployment model. Diamond decisions, rectangle outcomes. German labels, flowchart style.